TaskManager is a task manager in which you can add task, remove task, view task, check task
set task priority according to specified date or number of days from the current date.
It shows task in sorted manner in which Incompleted tasks are shown first according to their priorities.
priority and status are also mentioned.
Notify_today_task gives you notification regarding today's tasks.
You can also get task notification everytime you log-in by adding a command in .profile.